 public accountant and was a partner with the accounting firm of kpmg llp from  until his retirement in september  he is currently a board member of the william h hart realty company inc and the hart haven community association mr woollacott also served until  as a director of greencore us holdings a whollyowned subsidiary of greencore group plc an irish corporation listed on the irish stock exchange which is an international manufacturer of convenience foods and ingredients mr woollacott holds an executive master professional director certification from the american college of corporate directors qualifications the board of directors has concluded that mr woollacott should continue to serve as a director of the company because of his financial background and expertise gained through his career as partner of a large international public accounting firm as well as his experience on the board of an international company source brooks automation inc on    sign up for equilar atlas and view alfred woollacott iiis full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like alfred woollacott iii more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in alfred woollacott iiis network and community follow changes in alfred woollacott iiis employment and moneyinmotion connect with alfred woollacott iii through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example alfred woollacott iii alfred woollacott iiis connections  sign up now to view alfred woollacott iiis  connections » sandra n bane board member big  sporting goods corporation chong sup park lead independent director seagate technology plc amin j khoury chief executive officer and chairman of the board klx inc adam m michelin former board member cryoport inc joseph r martin board member brooks automation inc robert e anastasi former executive vice president global operations brooks automation inc terry